scenes.description: Koseki Bijou and her senpais (Kaela, Towa, Callie, Hakos Baelz) celebrate on stage.
Bijou is alone on stage, reflecting on the performance.
Bijou introduces her buddy, the 'Grand Executioner of Worlds' (Geo).
Bijou interacts with the audience about her 3D debut.
Bijou performs the 'Stick out your gyatt for the rizzler' dance.
Bijou prepares to make announcements with Geo.
Bijou announces her 3D Live merchandise (Room Slippers).
Bijou announces the final song of her debut.
